<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <table style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center; background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 10px;">
                <h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
                <p>Thank you for your order! We are pleased to confirm that your order has been successfully completed.</p>
                <p>Order Details:</p>
                <table style="width: 100%;">
                    {{!-- <tr>
                        <td><strong>Order Number:</strong></td>
                        <td>[OrderNumber]</td>
                    </tr> --}}
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Order Date:</strong></td>
                        <td>{{orderDate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Total Amount:</strong></td>
                        <td>{{totalAmount}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p>Your items will be shipped to the following address:</p>
                <p>{{address}}</p>
                <p>Thank you for choosing vKardz. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team.</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br> The vKardz Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 10px;">
                <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="https://wa.me/916377256382">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>

</html>
